{"tid":853253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑:楊潤雄越講越混淆，越說越無釐頭","createTime":"2018-10-08T12:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T14:20:39.000Z","uid":74778,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"987a80310cacb76c8bc567a9f58b98f394f0cc26","tid":853253,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"特區教育局局長楊潤雄忽然宣佈：香港特區「長遠」應該用普通話上語文課，用廣東話學中文，會令香港「喪失優勢」。<br />\n<br />\n然後局長又澄清，一切純屬「誤會」。<br />\n<br />\n越講越混淆，越說越無釐頭。與其半遮半掩、半推半就，一切務求清晰，不如由林鄭帶頭，首創：<br />\n<br />\n1，在立法會以普通話宣讀其「施政報告」；<br />\n<br />\n2，行政會議開會全用普通話；<br />\n<br />\n3，立法會內親中愛國議員即日起先改用普通話向政府官員提問，特首答問以普通話回答。<br />\n<br />\n4，響應導演張堅庭呼籲：特區政府官員子女，由即日起，全部不准讀香港的所謂國際學校，並拒絕去英國讀寄宿學校。<br />\n<br />\n你贊成嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/08/203920_6db9b0169e806bee0f96d61fa1aa8561.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F08%2F203920_6db9b0169e806bee0f96d61fa1aa8561.png&h=093ea3ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.533448593394335/2210407315698446/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftokit.channel%2Fphotos%2Fa.533448593394335%2F2210407315698446%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=agOrf3GLl%2FQ9LcKIXunToSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a36f95d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.533448593394335/2210407315698446/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"da96f76b425413b96e61496a81c17745b5f9f018","tid":853253,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">19老師，睇開D啦，賣港狗明知自己分狗糧就係幫共狗執屎同幫佢J完含乾淨架啦！！！！</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f1cc3f140207e2d8486a803c0363bafa704455","tid":853253,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"唔無厘頭日常生活會悶過係外國讀書架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82f1c3635fa85ae945bba332c092b5cdf397724","tid":853253,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"楊局腸係咪想幫萬億填海轉移視線呀？"},{"pid":"508e40d48be0e1483ac9f1042273ea06ce88fada","tid":853253,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"987a80310cacb76c8bc567a9f58b98f394f0cc26","tid":853253,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T12:39:32.000Z","msg":"特區教育局局長楊潤雄忽然宣佈：香港特區「長遠」應該用普通話上語文課，用廣東話學中文，會令香港「喪失優勢」。<br />\n<br />\n然後局長又澄清，一切純屬「誤會」。<br />\n<br />\n越講越混淆，越說越無釐頭。與其半遮半掩、半推半就，一切務求清晰，不如由林鄭帶頭，首創：<br />\n<br />\n1，在立法會以普通話宣讀其「施政報告」；<br />\n<br />\n2，行政會議開會全用普通話；<br />\n<br />\n3，立法會內親中愛國議員即日起先改用普通話向政府官員提問，特首答問以普通話回答。<br />\n<br />\n4，響應導演張堅庭呼籲：特區政府官員子女，由即日起，全部不准讀香港的所謂國際學校，並拒絕去英國讀寄宿學校。<br />\n<br />\n你贊成嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/08/203920_6db9b0169e806bee0f96d61fa1aa8561.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F08%2F203920_6db9b0169e806bee0f96d61fa1aa8561.png&h=093ea3ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.533448593394335/2210407315698446/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftokit.channel%2Fphotos%2Fa.533448593394335%2F2210407315698446%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=agOrf3GLl%2FQ9LcKIXunToSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a36f95d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/photos/a.533448593394335/2210407315698446/?type=3</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"乜你覺得賣港賊做唔出咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多咪讀到吹屎安咁"},{"pid":"4b37a1fac813f496ffe980c22327d2014812cc1e","tid":853253,"uid":51920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:20:40.000Z","msg":"呢D碎料<br />\n金融時報單野 <br />\n歐美都出晒聲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31fffac71bd864b55ac2631217a8a2d68dbe6d9","tid":853253,"uid":123308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:21:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">子女均讀國際學校</span>　楊潤雄稱因港教育制度「複雜」<br />\n</span><br />\n楊潤雄自上任教育局局長後，已屢次被質疑，其子女過去並非就讀主流地區學校。據了解，<span style=\"color: red;\">楊育有兩名子女，他們過去均就讀國際學校，目前則在澳洲讀大學。他昨日接受Now新聞台訪問，坦承兩名子女過去均就讀國際學校</span>，因為他派往外地工作回來後，覺得香港教育制度較「複雜」，而此舉亦「方便適應」。他表示希望將國際學校教學理念引入香港，但強調香港教育制度亦做出很多成績，在國際間備受推崇。他又認為自己其中一個子女，如果當年在傳統學校就讀，表現或會更好。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/128381/%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E5%9D%87%E8%AE%80%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E7%A8%B1%E5%9B%A0%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6-%E8%A4%87%E9%9B%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F128381%2F%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%259D%2587%25E8%25AE%2580%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1-%25E6%25A5%258A%25E6%25BD%25A4%25E9%259B%2584%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25BA%25A6-%25E8%25A4%2587%25E9%259B%259C&d=agOrf3GLl%2FQ9LcKIXunToSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=37d55484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/128381/%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E5%9D%87%E8%AE%80%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1-%E6%A5%8A%E6%BD%A4%E9%9B%84%E7%A8%B1%E5%9B%A0%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6-%E8%A4%87%E9%9B%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">豈有此理，暗中安排子女勾結外國勢力<br />\n去外地讀書，受洋鬼子資本主義教育涂毒！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪想反動！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"d157b6f1d094eb71f8f173cc5282365edcd1f7f3","tid":853253,"uid":111241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T13:34:19.000Z","msg":"等睇今晚教主屌染楊局長"},{"pid":"d05b4eb47c90a5854fc90d1ec33b2b6ff18df677","tid":853253,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T14:20:39.000Z","msg":"辭職畀蔡若蓮上啦"}]}